# Component Library — Trika Yoga & Wellness

Reusable components with **unique visual identities**. Never duplicate the same layout pattern on one page.

## Homepage Sections (each structurally different)

| Component | Layout — NOT a card grid |
|-----------|--------------------------|
| `CinematicHero` | Full-screen video, huge stacked typography, sound-wave viz, minimal nav |
| `EditorialFounderStory` | Full-screen portrait, magazine typography, timeline |
| `NervousSystemJourney` | Interactive scroll — hyper-arousal → burnout → restoration |
| `ImmersiveServicePanel` | Numbered full-bleed panels (01, 02, 03) — Apple storytelling |
| `CorporateDarkSection` | Black bg, large metrics (70%), executive programs |
| `HorizontalRetreatStory` | Horizontal scroll — Jaisalmer → Rishikesh → Gangtok → Sri Lanka |
| `PolaroidTestimonialWall` | Floating rotated cards, paper texture — NO slider |
| `ArchitecturalContact` | Vast whitespace, single statement, minimal form |

## Landing Page Components

`LandingHero` · `ProblemSymptomBlock` · `TransformationReveal` · `MethodologySection` · `LandingCTA`

Each landing page uses problem-first copy structure (see copy-guidelines).

## Rules

- ❌ No `ServiceCard` grids on homepage
- ❌ No testimonial sliders
- ❌ No Heading + Text + Button repeated stacks
- ✅ Each section = different composition

